# Grew 491→510 in TASK-#207 SLASH-FILES (added ShowFilePicker variant +
# file_picker field + Default init). Root cause is the dual-TuiEvent-
# enum structure: events.rs holds the canonical layer-0 definition AND
# app.rs holds a parallel duplicate that consumers import via
# `archon_tui::app::TuiEvent`. Adding any new variant requires editing
# both. The structural fix is to delete the app.rs duplicate and
# `pub use crate::events::TuiEvent;` instead — that's a cross-cutting
# refactor (touches every consumer's import path) and out of scope for
# #207's wrapper-scope ticket. Allowlisted here; consolidation
# follow-up tracked.
crates/archon-tui/src/app.rs

